data.description: Welcome to this charming three bedroom, two bath house located in Haltom City, boasting a generous 1485 square feet of living space. Built in 1969, this delightful home exudes a timeless appeal and offers a perfect blend of modern upgrades and classic features.As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere created by the well-maintained LVP flooring that flows seamlessly throughout the home. The kitchen has been upgraded with a gas cooktop and all new granite countertops. The primary bedroom is a serene retreat, offering a peaceful oasis for rest and rejuvenation. It features an en-suite bath with a walk-in shower. The two additional bedrooms are sizeable and provide abundant space for comfortable living, whether it's utilized as sleeping quarters, a home office, or a hobby room. Situated in Haltom City, this home benefits from a prime location with easy access to nearby amenities, including shopping centers, dining options, and recreational parks.
